<div class="column container">
  <div class="row">
    <h1 class="centered">hair cutting and styling services</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="row centered">
    <Service::Description
      @title="haircuts"
      @priceRange="$40 - $90"
      @image="services/petite-salon-haircut.png">
      <p>Experience a stunning haircut with a new level of expertise from our highly trained Petite Salon stylists. Whether you love your hair short, long, or layered let our stylists collaborate with you to create the haircut of your dreams, that fits your look and lifestyle. </p>
      <p>Our stylist will take into consideration texture and hair type, to truly craft a haircut that focuses on showing off your best features. </p>
      <p>Knowledge of trends and techniques are constantly being updated to bring you the very best in hair from our independent service providers.</p>
    </Service::Description>
    <Service::Description
      @title="blowouts"
      @priceRange="$40 - $65"
      @image="services/petite-salon-blowout.jpg">
      <p class="warning">Due to COVID-19 some blowdry services are being limited right now.  See our <LinkTo @route="covid-policy">health and safety policy</LinkTo></p>
      <p>The smooth, silky blow out is here for you at Petite. Who wants to style their hair on their own anyway, when you can have a talented stylist execute a stunning blow out for lasting style? It’s truly an art with a round brush and blow dryer, in our humble opinion. We’ve got you covered from root to ends.</p>
      <p>Have your blow out super straight and sleek, with a slight wave, or even a little beachy, if that’s your desire. This is a service that most discerning women schedule on a weekly basis or even every three days. Our Petite blow out includes luxury wash and finishing blow out style.</p>
    </Service::Description>
  </div>
  <div class="row centered">
    <Service::Description
      @title="updo's"
      @priceRange="">
      <p>For event hair that shines the place to go is Petite. Our stylists are highly skilled at crafting an updo for special occasion hair that truly highlights your overall look.</p>
      <p>They will collaborate with your wants and needs, what you are wearing, with the goal to bring you a specialized look that’s all your own.</p>
      <p>No stiff updo’s here, but we’ll make sure your event hair does last for all day wear and through the evening.</p>
      <p>A formal style that’s anything but ordinary. Extraordinary updos for any occasion that take into account your hair type and texture. In our hands you’ll find the updo that’s perfectly delivered each and every time.</p>
    </Service::Description>
    <Service::Description
      @title="special event styling"
      @priceRange="">
      <p>No pressure here, it’s just a huge day.</p>
      <strong>Your special event updo is a significant part of your special day look that our stylists are happy to be a part of.</strong>
      <p>Whatever your hair goals are, whether it’s romantically up or half and half, it’s going to be a splendid part of your day.</p>
      <p>We know how the photographs will tell the tale in the years to come, so we’ll collaborate with you on the perfect style to showcase your hair, veil headpiece, and features.</p>
      <p>Be the beautiful person you know you can be, with an updo that has star quality.</p>
    </Service::Description>

  </div>
  <div class="row centered">
    <Service::Description
      @title="smoothing treatments"
      @priceRange="">
      <p>Otherwise known as keratin or Brazilian straightening treatments, our technique and execution on this service is top notch.</p>
      <p>It has to be done just the right way to give you the full straight and sleek treatment for months to come.</p>
      <p>Prepare to sit for at least 90 minutes on this service that will last up to two to three months.</p>
      <p>Banish frizz, smooth out the hair cuticle, and get the extraordinarily chic and straight hair people will notice. </p>
      <p>This makes it a snap to do your hair in the mornings, if you normally have some unwanted wavy texture issues.</p>
    </Service::Description>
    <Service::Description
      @title="perm's"
      @priceRange="">
      <p>If you still want to give your hair excellent body and wave, a perm or “curl enhancing” treatment is still the go-to move to make with our skilled stylists. </p>
      <p>In their hands, you’ll walk away with splendidly created texture and curl or wave pattern, that will last for up to six months. Gorgeous and chic, a perm is the ultimate way to make your hair one of your best accessories.</p>
      <p>Old fashioned it’s not, so if you want an enhanced body of hair let the perm make this happen for you.</p>
      <p>Includes luxury wash, service, and a finished style.</p>
    </Service::Description>
  </div>
  <div class="row centered">
    <Service::Description
      @title="hair extensions"
      {{!-- @image="services/petite-salon-hair-extension.jpg" --}}
      @priceRange="">
      <p>Hair extensions are the fastest way to add head-turning drama. Natural hair tape-in or bonded, indulge in enviable volume and length.</p>
    </Service::Description>
    <Service::Description
      @title="conditioning treatments">
      <p>Overuse of heat and styling products, environmental toxins and chemicals from hair coloring can all damage and strip your hair of it’s natural shine.  We provide multiple treatments to protect and repair your hair. </p>
    </Service::Description>
  </div>
</div>